OL,3,CInquest: Failings at Barnet Hospital
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of 20-year-old
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FAn inquest has found multiple failings
OL,8,Fat Barnet Hospital contributed to the
OL,9,Fdeath of a 20-year-old woman who was
OL,10,Fsent home with undiagnosed meningitis.
OL,12,FSophie Ward went to hospital after
OL,13,Ffeeling symptoms including pain in her
OL,14,Fhead and neck, a fever, and
OL,15,Fsensitivity to light.
OL,17,FShe was misdiagnosed and sent home but
OL,18,Fdied of meningitis septicemia less
OL,19,Fthan 24 hours later.
