OL,3,CInquest: Failings at Barnet Hospital
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of 20-year-old
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FA jury at Barnet Coroners Court
OL,8,Freached a narrative conclusion on
OL,9,FFriday, finding that the decision to
OL,10,Fdischarge Sophie, not to administer
OL,11,Fantibiotics and the record keeping at
OL,12,FBarnet hospital all "more than
OL,13,Fminimally contributed to her death".
OL,15,FSophie's mother, Alice Ward said she
OL,16,Ftook her daughter to A&E after being
OL,17,Fdirected to do so by the NHS 111
OL,18,Fservice.
