OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FFor Sophie's sister Anna, while the
OL,8,Fcourt ruling was welcome, it also
OL,9,Fadded to her sense of loss.
OL,11,F"For someone who was so amazing to
OL,12,Fonly be dead because the fault of
OL,13,Fsomeone with no knowledge of sepsis,
OL,14,Fat an organisation that is disordered
OL,15,Fand doesn't work, makes a death even
OL,16,Fsadder." she said.
OL,18,FThe strain of meningitis Sophie had
OL,19,Fwas not part of routine vaccinations.
OL,20,FIt was only introduced into them in
OL,21,F2015.
