OL,4,Ccontributed to death of 20-year-old
OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,FThe Ward family now want to raise
OL,8,Fawareness of the symptoms of
OL,9,Fmeningitis and are calling for changes
OL,10,Fto be made at Barnet Hospital.
OL,12,FSophie's father Paul said: "If there's
OL,13,Fsomething that we want to come out of
OL,14,Fthis, it's that this happens to no
OL,15,Fother person in Barnet Hospital or
OL,16,Felsewhere because meningitis - if it's
OL,17,Ftreated at an early stage - is
OL,18,Ftreatable.
OL,20,F"But it has to be done with the
OL,21,Fgreatest urgency."
