OL,7,FA spokesperson from the Royal Free NHS
OL,8,FTrust, which runs Barnet Hospital,
OL,9,Fsaid: "We would like to share our
OL,10,Fdeepest condolences with Sophie's
OL,11,Ffamily and to apologise to them that
OL,12,FSophie died while under our care.
OL,14,F"We take the findings of the jury in
OL,15,Fthis inquest extremely seriously and
OL,16,Fwill carefully review the evidence
OL,17,Fthat has been heard along with the
OL,18,Frecord of inquest.
