OL,5,Cwoman
OL,7,F"Steps have been taken to improve
OL,8,Fsepsis and meningitis awareness among
OL,9,Four medical staff, including holding a
OL,10,Fstaff learning event to hear from both
OL,11,FSophie's family and the Meningitis
OL,12,FResearch Foundation.
OL,14,F"We also continue to remind emergency
OL,15,Fdepartment staff that senior doctors
OL,16,Fare available for advice and to
OL,17,Femphasise the importance of listening
OL,18,Fto the concerns of patients and
OL,19,Ffamilies."
